{"id":"5436","name":"cool-end-to-national-ice-cream-month-free-bravo-gelato-on-saturday","title":"Cool End To National Ice Cream Month: Free Bravo Gelato On Saturday","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2010-07-28T11:00:00-05:00","tags":["bravo gelato","freebies","ice cream","national ice cream month"],"categories":["Featured","Food &amp; Drink"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/scribebytrade/4471240008/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4043/4471240008_f7b88d3cf9.jpg\" alt=\"\"> </a></p><p>No one celebrates National Ice Cream Month quite like <a href=\"http://bravogelato.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;bravogelato.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Bravo Gelato</a>. If you don&#x2019;t <a href=\"http://twitter.com/BravoGelatoNash\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;twitter.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">follow them on Twitter</a> (<a href=\"http://twitter.com/BravoGelatoNash\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;twitter.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">@BravoGelatoNash</a>), you&#x2019;ve probably missed out on the fantastic deals they&#x2019;ve been offering every day this month at their Village Green location &#x2013; Buy one get one free, quarts for the price of pints, large for the price of a small&#x2026; We could go on and on. And with flavors like S&#x2019;more, Cinnamon Cayenne Chocolate Chip, Maple Benton&#x2019;s Bacon, Pina Colada, Cruze Dairy Buttermilk, Chocolate Hazelnut and Apple Pie, who can resist those kind of deals?</p><p>To top off National Ice Cream Month, Bravo Gelato will give away 1 regular sized gelato per person for FREE this Saturday, July 31 from 12-3pm at their Village Green location (off Hillsboro in the Green Hills Christie Cookie). All you have to do is show up! They&#x2019;ll be featuring an assortment of locally-themed flavors for the special occasion. Think flavors with Yazoo, Olive &amp; Sinclair, Jack Daniels and more.</p><p>If you haven&#x2019;t been to Bravo Gelato yet, Saturday is a great time to get your feet wet in the wonderful world of gelato. But we&#x2019;re warning you &#x2013; You&#x2019;ll probably get hooked. Don&#x2019;t just take our word for it&#x2026; Our blogging friends over at <a href=\"http://www.styleblueprint.com/interests/food-and-entertaining/bravo-gelato-free-saturday/?doing_wp_cron\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.styleblueprint.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Style Blueprint</a>, <a href=\"http://www.erinsfoodfiles.com/2010/03/bravo-gelato.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.erinsfoodfiles.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Erin&#x2019;s Food Files</a>, <a href=\"http://betheats.blogspot.com/2010/04/tweet-me-right-bravo-gelato.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;betheats.blogspot.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Eat. Drink. Smile.</a>, <a href=\"http://www.thebeersnob.com/2010/03/19/bravo-gelato-nashville-and-yazoo-brewery-two-great-tastes-that-taste-great-together/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.thebeersnob.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The Beer Snob</a> and <a href=\"http://nashvillefoodiesblog.com/2010/03/bravo-gelato/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillefoodiesblog.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville Foodies</a> can back up our claims.</p><p><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/scribebytrade/4471240008/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>christyfrink</em></a><em>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/02/19/national-holidays-we-like-free-pancake-free-pretzel-day-freebies/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: National Holidays We Like: Free Pancake &amp; Free Pretzel Day [Freebies]\">National Holidays We Like: Free Pancake &amp; Free Pretzel Day [Freebies]</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/09/25/aw-how-sweet-cold-stone-creamery-ice-cream-social-freebies/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Aw, How Sweet: Cold Stone Creamery Ice Cream Social [Freebies]\">Aw, How Sweet: Cold Stone Creamery Ice Cream Social [Freebies]</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/05/20/free-ice-cream-today-at-dippin-dots/\" rel=